   * </tr>
   * <tr>
   * <td>vendor</td>
   * <td>Optional string identifying the vendor.</td>
   * </tr>
   * <tr>
   * <td>version</td>
   * <td>Optional string identifying the version.</td>
   * </tr>
   * </table><p>
   *
